s/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚好食<br />\n<br />\n燒條魚，生雞蛋，魚子，少少魚生，<br />\n兩桶飯都食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申，係九州試過</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁大工程。。好難自己喺屋企整</blockquote><br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/151542_f1c969ae73e0c112a87e61647eda27e1.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F151542_f1c969ae73e0c112a87e61647eda27e1.jpg%22&d=jPjrKJtAGpYsYpGlKOq8YAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=96b87a90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/151542_f1c969ae73e0c112a87e61647eda27e1.jpg&quot;</a>  /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到我想去日本。。"},{"pid":"61aaabb5f658d83153a8e72469a6e6e4d5c1108f","tid":278074,"uid":82007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:22:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>扮日本人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係，呢個想法嘅靈感真係黎自日本人</blockquote><br />\n其實一定係中國人先<br />\n不過而家食早飯係日本流行過中國就真既"},{"pid":"3f380150a92782dea5faac03307846ba3d031e9d","tid":278074,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日本果D早餐，我食佢好撚多飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚好食<br />\n<br />\n燒條魚，生雞蛋，魚子，少少魚生，<br />\n兩桶飯都食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申，係九州試過</blockquote><